short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Modify YouTube thumbnails to include Arlo

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Is your browser experience boring? Are you having
trouble finding engaging blue-monster videos?

Butternut Squash? Yes, Please!

A fork of MrBeastify-Youtube that adds Arlo to every thumbnail.

Check the Github if you have any issues with functionality.

Not affiliated with Youtube or Arlo.

Source: https://github.com/Sprigazalea/Arloify-Youtube
